orn in 1569, in Barnstaple, Devon, England, United Kingdom as the son of George Baylegh. He married Agnes Sweete on 28 July 1593, in Barnstaple, Devon, England, United Kingdom."},"et":{"1569–":"1569–Surnud","1569–Male":"1569–Surnud","1562–1622":"1562–1622","1573–Female":"1573–Surnud","1598–1697":"1598–1697","–Male":"Surnud","1569":"1569","1622":"1622","16 OCT 1569":"16. oktoober 1569","1598":"1598","1697":"1697","28Jul1593":"28. juuli 1593","1573":"1573","1562":"1562","Barnstaple,Devon,England":"Barnstaple, Devon, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Barnstaple, Devon, England":"Barnstaple, Devon, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Barnstaple, Devonshire, England":"Barnstaple, Devon, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Manor, Peebles-shire, Scotland, United Kingdom":"Manor, Peeblesshire, Šotimaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1569–":"1569–Kuollut","1569–Male":"1569–Kuollut","1562–1622":"1562–1622","1573–Female":"1573–Kuollut","1598–1697":"1598–1697","–Male":"Kuollut","1569":"1569","1622":"1622","16 OCT 1569":"16. lokakuuta 1569","1598":"1598","1697":"1697","28Jul1593":"28. heinäkuuta 1593","1573":"1573","1562":"1562","Barnstaple,Devon,England":"Barnstaple, Devon, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Barnstaple, Devon, England":"Barnstaple, Devon, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Barnstaple, Devonshire, England":"Barnstaple, Devon, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Manor, Peebles-shire, Scotland, United Kingdom":"Manor, Peeblesshire, Skotlanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1569–":"1569–Décédé","1569–Male":"1569–Décédé","1562–1622":"1562–1622","1573–Female":"1573–Décédée","1598–1697":"1598–1697","–Male":"Décédé","1569":"1569","1622":"1622","16 OCT 1569":"16 octobre 1569","1598":"1598","1697":"1697","28Jul1593":"28 juillet 1593","1573":"1573","1562":"1562","Barnstaple,Devon,England":"Barnstaple, Devon, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Barnstaple, Devon, England":"Barnstaple, Devon, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Barnstaple, Devonshire, England":"Barnstaple, Devon, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Manor, P